Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OK了 小言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快速召唤 特大号水族箱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 鸽子?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等下…言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小言叶 水族箱变成鸽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？ 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,町中的各位居民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,本日 在樱新町商店街大道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,将举行樱花祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位叫上朋友 一同赏光参加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 寻人中心以及护疗休息处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,设置在比泉生活协商事务所前的临时帐篷中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在此之外 如遇到什么困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请联络比泉生活协商事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢金鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do yo need any help?\N需要什么帮助吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 诶？会说日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人叫言叶 我叫桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,知道爸爸妈妈在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 过得还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,二丁目没问题…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿姬的笔记耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,「姬笔记」耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,工作中请叫我「町长」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了 町长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是樱花祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请在行动中多考虑一下自己町长的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我说得跟个坏孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在担心大小姐的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,叫町长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,町长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,三丁目的工作已经结束了 会场那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小言叶 吵死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上把
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小言叶玩过这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们见识见识「樱新町黄金之手」的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,阿…原来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要轻轻地下去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,假的吧…小言叶就这点水平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前都看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,塑料制102毫米有柄环形框上 付4号水溶性薄纸的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,名称「纸网」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,耍赖 小言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不能耍诈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…吓到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那个叫做「言灵」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是能把嘴上说的东西变成实物的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我是半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 差不多就是半个妖怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…你是第一次来这个城市?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 来尝尝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,#&*@#%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 阿姬 还有哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐 不…町长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经吃了不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,人家的好意应该心怀感激地接受才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,迷路的儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,以为她爸妈会回来找 都等半天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是町长抢樱姬 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？问我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是人类哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才用言灵的时候好像吓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这个城市啊 是人类和妖怪共同生活的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,远处那个像大柱子一样的东西 看得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那是叫做「七乡」的七棵大樱树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪们啊 一这些高大的樱树为指向标 来到这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 在这里安心地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,其他城市大概看不到妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在这里可能会吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是外国人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪和人类啊 其实就像你跟我之间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,外国人跟日本人之间的差距差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么困难的话 随时可以跟我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真有阿姬的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,去找你父母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得在哪分开的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就带她去秋名那里 让小蓝看看再找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就带她去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个就继续巡视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟像她一样从市外来的客人还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事的话尽快联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,四丁目就拜托恭助了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是 大…町长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,七乡祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人反胃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一群什么都不知道的家伙过得倒悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,先给你们个下马威吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,暂且 先来个轻点的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(584,93.333)}寻人中心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,男儿有泪不轻弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不然会没女生追的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他是因为水奈不借他游戏机玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,吃点心咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所长亲手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,给 是樱饼~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不准拿别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,慢死了 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一直找不到人换班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名君 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当警察也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 城市热闹起来是件值得高兴的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然把我扔在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是走丢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 别生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,回去路上买些刁鱼烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要买就买大阪烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 蓝 可以去休息会儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该很想去祭典上逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你说什么呢 工作优先啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是事务所工作人员嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,原来已经逛过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名先生 我来送外卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…发票上写的要我在这个时间送来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我点的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是姬小姐点的啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,时间正好 和我预想得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,记得自己掏钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子好像和父母走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,能拜托蓝看一下 找找她父母吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这里的所长 比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,给你吃好吃的樱饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在···在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,能看看这孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来 和姐姐一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不是 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,能找到她父亲或者母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…怎…怎么办好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,姬她们好像找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫七海蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有一种称作「觉」的 可以读取别人内心的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让我稍微看一下你在想的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,脑中想一想爸爸妈妈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要说看到…倒算是看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是蓝的画工吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看到的真是这样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝 是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名 是妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这是…堕化?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这…小言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华 带大家去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我来拖住着家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏选在祭典这天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那个可恶的猫眼男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好赏个花就不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这堕化还真是土到掉渣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只是试探吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要出手哦 八重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,静静地守望就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了土地神的本分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,巨大的金鱼在发飙?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 请不要慌张 请保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就你自己在慌吧 这根本没人慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,之后交给我们就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那条鱼就拜托小桃华了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我这没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,代我向阿姬她们问好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快速召唤 篮子篮子篮子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,报刚才的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快速召唤 特大号纸网
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,解决咯 阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让我开心开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再陪我玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也出现巨大金鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如此频繁的堕化…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我等下再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少条
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一…二…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,广域读心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定了 一个有八条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,八条?好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,话说…蓝…你是不是在吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 确切地点在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK了 小言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等死我了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快速召唤 特大号水族箱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特大号水族箱···特大号水族箱···
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,鸽子?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等下…言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小言叶 水族箱变成鸽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,云切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,十四段 火消
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我来做你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,异能的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是纯种的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的荧光棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在 阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给我飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快速召唤 金鱼缸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮 言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这边搞定后 就去市里帮忙善后哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,见过他们后有何感想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来呢 要来场和睦的作战会议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,反正很快会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要什么计谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可没有机关和障眼法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,人类和妖怪的巅峰对决哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明明输过一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小言叶 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 春风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:38.01,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:42.73,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.10,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}やあ また会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ねぇ こんばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.40,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}いや こんにちはだって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.94,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}広いようで 狭いようで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}退屈はいらないみたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.53,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}あぁ 問題は依然あって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.57,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}頭痛いんだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.99,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}少しずつって言い聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:04.16,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}願い事叶えて行きましょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:08.21,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}I shall remember I wanna do I shall remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:14.05,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}拾い集めた後悔のかけらたちを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.30,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}夜が明ける前に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:20.31,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何遍を貼って 並べてて 希望に変える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.85,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}10秒継続中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:26.85,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}桜が去つて散ったその後で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何が真実なのかは かるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.49,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody そう今は奏でて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.41,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}愛が世界救うのだなんて 僕は信じてないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:45.08,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今 目の前の君が 明日を生きれるくらいには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.37,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.88,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不条理は吹き飛ばしていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:50.17,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀楽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:53.63,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}大丈夫さ　どこまでもゆくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:59.09,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalala　lalalalalala!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.87,edch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.10,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呀啊 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呐 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.40,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不 应该是中午好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.94,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}好像很宽敞 又好像很拥挤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过貌似和「无聊」二字无缘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.53,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}啊 问题依然还在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.57,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}真是让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.99,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过还是向我慢慢道来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:04.16,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我们一起去实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:14.05,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将散落一地的后悔的碎片小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.30,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在天明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:20.31,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}一遍遍地粘合 一遍遍地重排 将之变为希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.85,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}持续10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:26.85,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在那满树樱花逝去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}什么才是真实 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.49,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody 没错 现在就奏响吧
